<Paragraph>
 Tab navigation control facilitates the display of pages/items (with transition effects) like an Ad rotator in web applications, thereby enhancing the UI look and feel.  It supports only .NET framework version 4.0. 
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph  TextAlignment ="Center">
  <Image Source="Images\TabNavigationControl.png" Stretch="None" />
</Paragraph>
   

